<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mk">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"/>
  <title>🌍 Makedon Eco World – Светска Платформа за Собирање Шишиња</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Собирај шишиња, добивај EcoPoints, конвертирај во пари или награди. Глобално. Безбедно. Автоматизирано."/>
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#2ecc71"/>
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"/>
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent"/>
  <link rel="manifest" href="data:application/json,{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Makedon Eco World&quot;,&quot;short_name&quot;:&quot;EcoWorld&quot;,&quot;start_url&quot;:&quot;/&quot;,&quot;display&quot;:&quot;standalone&quot;,&quot;background_color&quot;:&quot;#f8f9fa&quot;,&quot;theme_color&quot;:&quot;#2ecc71&quot;,&quot;icons&quot;:[{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'%3E%3Ctext y='.9em' font-size='90'%3E🌱%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:&quot;192x192&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/svg+xml&quot;}]}"/>
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'%3E%3Ctext y='.9em' font-size='90'%3E🌱%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>
  
  <!-- Eco Translate Module (Fixed for GitHub Pages) -->
  <script src="./src/services/eco-translate.js"></script>
  <script>
    // Иницијализација на преводот после вчитување
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      if (typeof window.EcoTranslate !== 'undefined') {
        window.ecoTranslate = new window.EcoTranslate({ defaultLang: 'mk' });
        // Пополни го селекторот за јазик
        const selector = document.getElementById('language-selector');
        if (selector && window.ecoTranslate?.config?.languages) {
          for (const [code, name] of Object.entries(window.ecoTranslate.config.languages)) {
            const option = document.createElement('option');
            option.value = code;
            option.textContent = name;
            if (code === (window.ecoTranslate.currentLang || 'mk')) option.selected = true;
            selector.appendChild(option);
          }
          selector.addEventListener('change', async function(e) {
            if (typeof window.ecoTranslate.setLanguage === 'function') {
              await window.ecoTranslate.setLanguage(e.target.value);
              // Преведи ги елементите со data-translate-key
              const elements = document.querySelectorAll('[data-translate-key]');
              if (elements.length > 0 && window.ecoTranslateInstance) {
                await window.ecoTranslateInstance.translateUI(Array.from(elements), e.target.value);
              }
            }
          });
        }
      }
    });
  </script>
  
  <style>
    :root{--primary:#2ecc71;--primary-dark:#27ae60;--secondary:#3498db;--accent:#f39c12;--dark:#2c3e50;--light:#ecf0f1;--danger:#e74c3c;--success:#2ecc71;--gradient:linear-gradient(135deg,#2ecc71 0%,#3498db 50%,#9b59b6 100%);--shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.15);--card-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);--border-radius:16px;--transition:all .3s cubic-bezier(.175,.885,.32,1.27)}
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Geneva,Verdana,sans-serif;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8f9fa 0%,#e8f5e9 50%,#d4edda 100%);color:var(--dark);line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden;min-height:100vh}
    .container{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}
    
    /* ===== HEADER ===== */
    header{background:var(--gradient);color:#fff;padding:1rem 0;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:1000;box-shadow:var(--shadow);backdrop-filter:blur(10px)}
    .header-content{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem}
    .logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer}
    .logo i{font-size:2.2rem;animation:pulse 2s infinite}
    .logo span{background:linear-gradient(to right,#fff,#e0f7fa);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
    nav ul{display:flex;list-style:none;gap:1rem}
    nav a{color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:25px;transition:var(--transition);position:relative}
    nav a:hover,nav a.active{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2)}
    nav a.active:after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-5px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:8px;height:8px;background:#fff;border-radius:50%}
    .auth-buttons{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .btn{padding:10px 24px;border:none;border-radius:50px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .btn:before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:-100%;width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.3),transparent);transition:left .5s}
    .btn:hover:before{left:100%}
    .btn-primary{background:#fff;color:var(--primary);box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
    .btn-outline{background:transparent;border:2px solid #fff;color:#fff}
    .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
    .btn:active{transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .btn:disabled{opacity:.6;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none}
    
    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    .hero{padding:6rem 0 4rem;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .hero:before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-50%;right:-50%;width:200%;height:200%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(46,204,113,.1) 0%,transparent 70%);animation:rotate 20s linear infinite}
    @keyframes rotate{from{transform:rotate(0deg)}to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
    .hero h1{font-size:3.8rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;background:var(--gradient);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;line-height:1.1;position:relative;z-index:1;animation:fadeInUp .8s ease}
    @keyframes fadeInUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
    .hero p{font-size:1.45rem;max-width:850px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;color:var(--dark);position:relative;z-index:1;animation:fadeInUp .8s ease .2s both}
    .hero-stats{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:2rem;margin-top:3rem;flex-wrap:wrap;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .stat-card{background:#fff;padding:1.8rem 2rem;border-radius:var(--border-radius);box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);min-width:180px;text-align:center;transition:var(--transition);border:2px solid transparent}
    .stat-card:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);border-color:var(--primary)}
    .stat-number{font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);display:block;line-height:1}
    .stat-label{color:#666;font-weight:500;font-size:.95rem;margin-top:.5rem}
    
    /* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
    .section{padding:6rem 0;position:relative}
    .section:nth-child(even){background:#fff}
    .section-title{text-align:center;margin-bottom:4rem}
    .section-title h2{font-size:2.8rem;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:1rem;position:relative;display:inline-block}
    .section-title h2:after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-12px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:80px;height:4px;background:var(--gradient);border-radius:2px}
    .section-title p{color:#666;max-width:750px;margin:1.5rem auto 0;font-size:1.15rem}
    
    /* ===== CARDS GRID ===== */
    .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:2rem;margin-top:2rem}
    .card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--border-radius);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);transition:var(--transition);border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.05);position:relative}
    .card:hover{transform:translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);box-shadow:0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.15);z-index:10}
    .card-header{padding:1.8rem;background:var(--gradient);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
    .card-header .country-flag{font-size:2rem}
    .card-header .country-name{font-weight:700;font-size:1.25rem}
    .card-body{padding:1.8rem}
    .card-body p{color:#555;margin-bottom:1rem}
    .card-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;margin:1.2rem 0}
    .card-stat{text-align:center;padding:1rem;background:var(--light);border-radius:12px}
    .card-stat-value{font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);font-size:1.5rem;display:block}
    .card-stat-label{color:#666;font-size:.9rem}
    .best-practice{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f5e9,#d4edda);padding:1.2rem;border-radius:12px;border-left:4px solid var(--primary);margin-top:1rem;font-size:.95rem}
    .best-practice strong{color:var(--primary-dark)}
    
    /* ===== FEATURES ===== */
    .feature-card{text-align:center;padding:2.5rem 2rem;transition:var(--transition)}
    .feature-icon{width:90px;height:90px;background:var(--gradient);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.8rem;color:#fff;font-size:2.2rem;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(46,204,113,.3);transition:var(--transition)}
    .card:hover .feature-icon{transform:scale(1.1) rotate(5deg)}
    .feature-card h3{margin-bottom:1rem;color:var(--dark);font-size:1.4rem}
    .feature-card p{color:#666;font-size:1rem}
    
    /* ===== CALCULATOR ===== */
    .calculator{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:2.5rem;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);margin:2.5rem 0;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.05)}
    .calc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:1.8rem;margin-top:1.8rem}
    .calc-input label{font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);display:block;margin-bottom:.6rem;font-size:1rem}
    .calc-input input,.calc-input select{width:100%;padding:14px 16px;border:2px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:12px;font-size:1rem;transition:var(--transition);background:#fafafa}
    .calc-input input:focus,.calc-input select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--primary);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(46,204,113,.1)}
    .calc-result{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8f9fa,#e8f5e9);padding:2rem;border-radius:16px;text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;border:2px dashed var(--primary)}
    .calc-result-label{color:#666;font-size:1.1rem}
    .calc-result-value{font-size:3.2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);display:block;margin:.8rem 0;line-height:1;animation:pulse 2s infinite}
    @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{transform:scale(1)}50%{transform:scale(1.05)}}
    .calc-result-currency{color:var(--dark);font-weight:600;font-size:1.2rem}
    .calc-result-note{margin-top:1rem;color:#666;font-size:.95rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px}
    
    /* ===== PAYMENTS ===== */
    .payments{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:1.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:2.5rem}
    .payment-badge{background:#fff;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:50px;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);transition:var(--transition);border:2px solid transparent}
    .payment-badge:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:var(--primary)}
    .payment-badge i{font-size:1.6rem}
    .stripe{color:#635bff}.paypal{color:#003087}.visa{color:#1a1f71}.mastercard{color:#eb001b}
    
    /* ===== AI AGENTS ===== */
    .agent-card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);text-align:center;transition:var(--transition);border-top:4px solid var(--secondary);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .agent-card:hover{transform:translateY(-8px)}
    .agent-card:before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--gradient);opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}
    .agent-card:hover:before{opacity:1}
    .agent-card.qwen{border-top-color:#6366f1}.agent-card.gpt{border-top-color:#10a37f}.agent-card.claude{border-top-color:#d97757}.agent-card.harvey{border-top-color:#8b5cf6}
    .agent-icon{width:80px;height:80px;background:var(--light);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;font-size:2rem;color:var(--secondary);transition:var(--transition);box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
    .agent-card:hover .agent-icon{transform:scale(1.1)}
    .agent-card.qwen .agent-icon{color:#6366f1;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff,#dbeafe)}.agent-card.gpt .agent-icon{color:#10a37f;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ecfdf5,#d1fae5)}.agent-card.claude .agent-icon{color:#d97757;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff7ed,#fed7aa)}.agent-card.harvey .agent-icon{color:#8b5cf6;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f5f3ff,#e9d5ff)}
    .agent-card h4{margin-bottom:.8rem;color:var(--dark);font-size:1.3rem}
    .agent-card p{color:#666;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.5}
    .agent-status{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.85rem;margin-top:1rem;font-weight:500}
    .status-online{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d4edda,#c3e6cb);color:#155724}
    .status-processing{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff3cd,#ffeaa7);color:#856404}
    .status-offline{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8d7da,#f5c6cb);color:#721c24}
    
    /* ===== SECURITY ===== */
    .security-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;padding:1.5rem;background:#fff;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);margin-bottom:1rem;transition:var(--transition);border-left:4px solid var(--primary)}
    .security-item:hover{transform:translateX(5px)}
    .security-icon{width:48px;height:48px;background:var(--gradient);border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.3rem;flex-shrink:0;box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(46,204,113,.3)}
    .security-item h4{color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:.4rem;font-size:1.15rem}
    .security-item p{color:#666;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.5}
    
    /* ===== GAMIFICATION ===== */
    .gamification{background:var(--gradient);border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:3rem;color:#fff;margin-top:2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .gamification:before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-50%;right:-50%;width:200%;height:200%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,255,255,.15) 0%,transparent 70%);z-index:0;animation:rotate 25s linear infinite}
    .gamification-content{position:relative;z-index:1}
    .gamification h3{margin-bottom:1.2rem;font-size:2rem}
    .gamification p{opacity:.95;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 2rem;font-size:1.1rem}
    .levels{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:1.2rem;margin-top:1.8rem}
    .level-badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);padding:1.5rem 1rem;border-radius:16px;text-align:center;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);transition:var(--transition);border:2px solid transparent}
    .level-badge:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
    .level-badge.active{background:#fff;color:var(--dark);font-weight:600;transform:scale(1.08);border-color:var(--primary);box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
    .level-icon{font-size:2.2rem;margin-bottom:.8rem;display:block}
    .level-name{font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.3rem}
    .level-range{font-size:.85rem;opacity:.9}
    
    /* ===== CTA ===== */
    .cta{background:var(--gradient);padding:5rem 0;text-align:center;color:#fff;margin:4rem 0;border-radius:var(--border-radius);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .cta:before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%,rgba(255,255,255,.1) 0%,transparent 50%)}
    .cta h2{font-size:2.6rem;margin-bottom:1.8rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .cta p{max-width:750px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;font-size:1.2rem;opacity:.95;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .cta-buttons{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:1.2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .btn-cta{padding:16px 36px;font-size:1.15rem;border-radius:50px;font-weight:600}
    .btn-white{background:#fff;color:var(--primary);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
    .btn-outline-white{background:transparent;border:2px solid #fff;color:#fff}
    .btn-cta:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}
    
    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    footer{background:var(--dark);color:#fff;padding:4rem 0 2rem;margin-top:4rem}
    .footer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:2.5rem}
    .footer-col h3{margin-bottom:1.8rem;position:relative;padding-bottom:1rem;font-size:1.3rem}
    .footer-col h3:after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;width:45px;height:3px;background:var(--primary);border-radius:2px}
    .footer-col ul{list-style:none}
    .footer-col ul li{margin-bottom:1rem}
    .footer-col a{color:#ccc;text-decoration:none;transition:color .3s ease;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:1rem}
    .footer-col a:hover{color:var(--primary);transform:translateX(3px)}
    .footer-col a i{font-size:.8rem;opacity:.7}
    .social-links{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-top:1.5rem}
    .social-links a{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;transition:var(--transition);font-size:1.1rem}
    .social-links a:hover{background:var(--primary);transform:translateY(-4px) scale(1.1);box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(46,204,113,.4)}
    .copyright{text-align:center;padding-top:2.5rem;margin-top:2.5rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:#aaa;font-size:1rem}
    .copyright a{color:var(--primary);text-decoration:none}
    
    /* ===== MODALS ===== */
    .modal{display:none;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);z-index:2000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;animation:fadeIn .3s ease}
    .modal.active{display:flex}
    @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
    .modal-content{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:2.5rem;max-width:520px;width:100%;max-height:90vh;overflow-y:auto;position:relative;animation:slideUp .4s ease}
    @keyframes slideUp{from{transform:translateY(50px);opacity:0}to{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1}}
    .modal-close{position:absolute;top:1.2rem;right:1.2rem;background:none;border:none;font-size:2rem;cursor:pointer;color:#666;transition:var(--transition);width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
    .modal-close:hover{background:var(--light);color:var(--danger);transform:rotate(90deg)}
    
    /* ===== CAMERA SCAN ===== */
    #camera-preview{width:100%;max-height:320px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e,#16213e);border-radius:16px;margin:1.2rem 0;display:none;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    #camera-preview.active{display:block}
    #camera-preview:after{content:'';position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:80%;height:60%;border:3px dashed rgba(46,204,113,.7);border-radius:20px;pointer-events:none;animation:pulse-border 2s infinite}
    @keyframes pulse-border{0%,100%{border-color:rgba(46,204,113,.7)}50%{border-color:rgba(46,204,113,1)}}
    #scan-result{margin-top:1.5rem;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:16px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f5e9,#d4edda);display:none;animation:fadeInUp .4s ease}
    #scan-result.active{display:block}
    #scan-result.success{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d4edda,#c3e6cb);border:2px solid var(--success)}
    #scan-result.error{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8d7da,#f5c6cb);border:2px solid var(--danger)}
    
    /* ===== CONFETTI ===== */
    .confetti{position:fixed;width:10px;height:10px;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;border-radius:2px;animation:confetti-fall 3s ease-in-out forwards}
    @keyframes confetti-fall{0%{transform:translateY(-10vh) rotate(0deg) scale(1);opacity:1}100%{transform:translateY(100vh) rotate(720deg) scale(0);opacity:0}}
    
    /* ===== MAP ===== */
    #map{height:350px;width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin:1.5rem 0;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);border:3px solid #fff}
    .map-legend{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:1rem}
    .legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:.9rem;color:#666}
    .legend-dot{width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%}
    .legend-dot.pakomak{background:#2ecc71}.legend-dot.store{background:#3498db}.legend-dot.vending{background:#f39c12}.legend-dot.mall{background:#9b59b6}
    
    /* ===== PROGRESS BAR ===== */
    .progress-container{background:var(--light);border-radius:10px;height:8px;overflow:hidden;margin:1rem 0}
    .progress-bar{height:100%;background:var(--gradient);border-radius:10px;transition:width .5s ease;position:relative}
    .progress-bar:after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:3px;height:100%;background:#fff;animation:shine 1.5s infinite}
    @keyframes shine{0%{transform:translateX(-10px)}100%{transform:translateX(200px)}}
    
    /* ===== GLOBAL MALLS SECTION ===== */
    .mall-controls{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;align-items:center}
    .mall-search{position:relative;width:100%;max-width:500px}
    .mall-search i{position:absolute;left:16px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:#666}
    .mall-search input{width:100%;padding:14px 16px 14px 44px;border:2px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:12px;font-size:1rem;background:#fff;transition:var(--transition)}
    .mall-search input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--primary);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(46,204,113,.1)}
    .mall-tabs{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.6rem;justify-content:center}
    .mall-tab{padding:10px 18px;border:none;border-radius:50px;background:var(--light);color:var(--dark);font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition);font-size:.95rem}
    .mall-tab:hover{background:#d4edda}
    .mall-tab.active{background:var(--gradient);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(46,204,113,.3)}
    .mall-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:1.5rem}
    .mall-card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:1.5rem;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.04);transition:var(--transition);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.8rem}
    .mall-card:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
    .mall-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:start;gap:10px}
    .mall-name{font-weight:700;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--dark);line-height:1.3}
    .mall-priority{padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
    .priority-critical{background:#ffebee;color:#c62828;border:1px solid #ef9a9a}
    .priority-high{background:#e8f5e9;color:#2e7d32;border:1px solid #a5d6a7}
    .priority-medium{background:#fff3e0;color:#f57c00;border:1px solid #ffe0b2}
    .priority-low{background:#f5f5f5;color:#616161;border:1px solid #e0e0e0}
    .mall-meta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.8rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#555}
    .mall-meta span{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
    .mall-meta i{color:var(--primary);width:16px;text-align:center}
    .mall-region{font-size:.8rem;color:#888;font-weight:500;margin-top:auto}
    .mall-note{font-size:.85rem;color:#666;background:#f8f9fa;padding:.6rem .8rem;border-radius:8px;margin-top:.2rem}
    @media(max-width:768px){.mall-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.mall-controls{gap:1rem}}
    
    /* ===== LOCAL PARTNERS SECTION ===== */
    #local-partners .card { border-top: 4px solid var(--primary); }
    #local-partners .card-header { background: var(--gradient); }
    
    /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
    @media(max-width:1024px){.hero h1{font-size:3.2rem}.section-title h2{font-size:2.4rem}}
    @media(max-width:768px){.hero{padding:4rem 0 3rem}.hero h1{font-size:2.6rem}.hero p{font-size:1.2rem}.section{padding:4.5rem 0}.section-title h2{font-size:2rem}.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.header-content{flex-direction:column;text-align:center}nav ul{flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}.auth-buttons{width:100%;justify-content:center}.stat-card{min-width:140px;padding:1.4rem}.stat-number{font-size:2.2rem}.calc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.cta h2{font-size:2.2rem}.cta p{font-size:1.1rem}}
    @media(max-width:480px){.hero h1{font-size:2.2rem}.btn{padding:10px 20px;font-size:.95rem}.feature-icon{width:75px;height:75px;font-size:1.8rem}.agent-icon{width:70px;height:70px;font-size:1.7rem}}
    
    /* ===== ACCESSIBILITY ===== */
    @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){*,*::before,*::after{animation-duration:.01ms!important;animation-iteration-count:1!important;transition-duration:.01ms!important}}
    .sr-only{position:absolute;width:1px;height:1px;padding:0;margin:-1px;overflow:hidden;clip:rect(0,0,0,0);white-space:nowrap;border:0}
    
    /* ===== LOADING ===== */
    .loading{display:inline-block;width:20px;height:20px;border:3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);border-radius:50%;border-top-color:#fff;animation:spin 1s linear infinite;margin-right:8px}
    @keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
    .loading-dark{border-color:rgba(0,0,0,.3);border-top-color:var(--primary)}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- ===== HEADER ===== -->
  <header>
    <div class="container header-content">
      <div class="logo" onclick="scrollToTop()">
        <i class="fas fa-leaf floating"></i>
        <span data-translate-key="hero_title">Makedon Eco World</span>
      </div>
      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#" class="active" data-translate-key="nav_home">Дома</a></li>
          <li><a href="#global" data-translate-key="nav_global">Глобално</a></li>
          <li><a href="#features" data-translate-key="nav_features">Карактеристики</a></li>
          <li><a href="#financial" data-translate-key="nav_financial">Финансии</a></li>
          <li><a href="#global-malls" data-translate-key="nav_partners">Партнери</a></li>
          <li><a href="#ai" data-translate-key="nav_ai">AI Агенти</a></li>
          <li><a href="#security" data-translate-key="nav_security">Безбедност</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <div class="auth-buttons">
        <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="openModal('loginModal')"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> <span class="hide-mobile" data-translate-key="btn_login">Најави се</span></button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="startScan()"><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> <span class="hide-mobile" data-translate-key="btn_scan">Скенрај</span></button>
      </div>
      <select id="language-selector" style="margin-left:10px;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:20px;border:2px solid #fff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:#fff;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer">
        <option value="mk">🇲🇰 МК</option>
        <option value="en">🇬🇧 EN</option>
        <option value="sq">🇦🇱 SQ</option>
        <option value="sr">🇷🇸 SR</option>
        <option value="bg">🇧🇬 BG</option>
        <option value="de">🇩🇪 DE</option>
      </select>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 data-translate-key="hero_title">🌍 Makedon Eco World</h1>
      <p data-translate-key="hero_description">Првата светска платформа за собирање шишиња со глобална валутизација. Секој оставен предмет = 1 EcoPoint = Глобална вредност. Почиста планета, пополн џеб!</p>
      <div class="auth-buttons" style="justify-content:center;margin-top:1rem">
        <button class="btn btn-white btn-cta" onclick="startScan()" data-translate-key="btn_start_now"><i class="fas fa-play-circle"></i> Започни Сега</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-white btn-cta" onclick="scrollToSection('howItWorks')" data-translate-key="btn_learn_more"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Како Работи</button>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat-card"><span class="stat-number">60+</span><span class="stat-label" data-translate-key="stat_countries">Земји</span></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><span class="stat-number">98%</span><span class="stat-label" data-translate-key="stat_efficiency">Ефикасност</span></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><span class="stat-number">€0.25</span><span class="stat-label" data-translate-key="stat_average">Просек</span></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><span class="stat-number" id="userPoints">0</span><span class="stat-label" data-translate-key="stat_your_points">Твои Поени</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== GLOBAL ANALYSIS ===== -->
  <section class="section" id="global">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2 data-translate-key="section_global_title">🌐 Глобална Анализа: Најдобрите Практики</h2>
        <p data-translate-key="section_global_desc">Ги интегриравме срцевините од најдобрите системи ширум светот во нашата платформа.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <!-- Germany -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header"><span class="country-flag">🇩🇪</span><span class="country-name">Германија – Pfand</span></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p><strong>98%+ стапка на враќање</strong>. Моментална исплата преку автомати во секој супермаркет.</p>
            <div class="card-stats">
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">€0.25</span><span class="card-stat-label">Депозит</span></div>
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">98%</span><span class="card-stat-label">Враќање</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="best-practice"><strong>Срцевина за нас:</strong> Интеграција со малопродажба + моментална дигитална исплата преку паричници.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Norway -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header"><span class="country-flag">🇳🇴</span><span class="country-name">Норвешка – Infinitum</span></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p>Пионер во <strong>гејмификацијата</strong>. Бонуси, нивоа, социјални предизвици за максимална ангажираност.</p>
            <div class="card-stats">
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">92%</span><span class="card-stat-label">Враќање</span></div>
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">2-3 NOK</span><span class="card-stat-label">Депозит</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="best-practice"><strong>Срцевина за нас:</strong> Гејмификација + социјални елементи = долгорочна лојалност.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Lithuania -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header"><span class="country-flag">🇱🇹</span><span class="country-name">Литванија – Užstato</span></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p><strong>Мобилно-прво</strong> искуство. Скенрај, врати, добивај поени веднаш. Едноставно и брзо.</p>
            <div class="card-stats">
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">92%</span><span class="card-stat-label">Враќање</span></div>
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">€0.10</span><span class="card-stat-label">Депозит</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="best-practice"><strong>Срцевина за нас:</strong> Едноставен кориснички тек + брза мобилна верификација.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Macedonia -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header"><span class="country-flag">🇲🇰</span><span class="country-name">Македонија – Пакомак</span></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p>Непрофитна компанија со фокус на <strong>едукација</strong> и "зелени поени" за јавни услуги.</p>
            <div class="card-stats">
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">Пилот</span><span class="card-stat-label">Фаза</span></div>
              <div class="card-stat"><span class="card-stat-value">1:1</span><span class="card-stat-label">Сисе=Поен</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="best-practice"><strong>Срцевина за нас:</strong> Партнерства со локални бизниси + поени за јавни услуги.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FEATURES ===== -->
  <section class="section" id="features" style="background:#f8f9fa">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2 data-translate-key="section_features_title">✨ Карактеристики</h2>
        <p data-translate-key="section_features_desc">Секоја функција е дизајнирана да биде интуитивна, мотивирачка и глобално скалабилна.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i></div>
          <h3 data-translate-key="feature_scan_title">QR/Баркод Скенрање</h3>
          <p data-translate-key="feature_scan_desc">Скенрај го кодот на шишето/лименката. Нашиот AI веднаш го верификува и додава поени.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i></div>
          <h3 data-translate-key="feature_map_title">Мапа на Точки</h3>
          <p data-translate-key="feature_map_desc">Најди најблиски контејнери, автомати или партнерски локации со геолокација.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i></div>
          <h3 data-translate-key="feature_portfolio_title">Портфолио со Поени</h3>
          <p data-translate-key="feature_portfolio_desc">Следи ги твоите EcoPoints, види историја, конвертирај во пари, ваучери или донации.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i></div>
          <h3 data-translate-key="feature_gamification_title">Гејмификација</h3>
          <p data-translate-key="feature_gamification_desc">Освојувај нивоа, беџови и се натпреварувај со пријатели на глобални лидерборди.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i></div>
          <h3 data-translate-key="feature_donations_title">Донации за Екологија</h3>
          <p data-translate-key="feature_donations_desc">Претвори ги поените во донации за шуми, океани или локални еколошки проекти.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
          <h3 data-translate-key="feature_social_title">Социјални Предизвици</h3>
          <p data-translate-key="feature_social_desc">Создади тим со пријатели, постави заеднички цели и освојувај бонус поени.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Calculator -->
      <div class="calculator">
        <h3 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:1rem;color:var(--dark);font-size:1.6rem"><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> <span data-translate-key="calculator_title">Калкулатор: Колку Можеш Да Заработиш?</span></h3>
        <p style="text-align:center;color:#666;margin-bottom:1.5rem" data-translate-key="calculator_desc">Внеси колку шишиња/лименки собираш неделно и види ја твојата потенцијална заработка.</p>
        <div class="calc-grid">
          <div class="calc-input">
            <label for="bottles">🍶 <span data-translate-key="calc_bottles">Шишиња неделно</span></label>
            <input type="number" id="bottles" placeholder="на пр. 10" min="0" value="10">
          </div>
          <div class="calc-input">
            <label for="cans">🥫 <span data-translate-key="calc_cans">Лименки неделно</span></label>
            <input type="number" id="cans" placeholder="на пр. 15" min="0" value="15">
          </div>
          <div class="calc-input">
            <label for="country">🌍 <span data-translate-key="calc_country">Земја за конверзија</span></label>
            <select id="country">
              <option value="mk">🇲🇰 Северна Македонија</option>
              <option value="de">🇩🇪 Германија</option>
              <option value="no">🇳🇴 Норвешка</option>
              <option value="us">🇺🇸 САД</option>
              <option value="global">🌐 Глобално (средно)</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="calc-result">
          <span class="calc-result-label" data-translate-key="calc_result_label">Твојата неделна заработка:</span>
          <span class="calc-result-value" id="resultValue">€3.75</span>
          <span class="calc-result-currency"><span data-translate-key="calc_or">или</span> <span id="resultPoints">25</span> EcoPoints</span>
          <p class="calc-result-note"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> <span data-translate-key="calc_note">Вредноста варира според локалниот депозит. Платформата автоматски ја конвертира.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Map Preview -->
      <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);margin-top:2.5rem">
        <h3 style="color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:1rem;text-align:center;font-size:1.5rem"><i class="fas fa-globe-europe"></i> <span data-translate-key="map_title">Глобална Мрежа на Точки</span></h3>
        <p style="color:#666;text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem" data-translate-key="map_desc">Платформата автоматски ги прикажува најблиските точки за враќање шишиња, без разлика каде си.</p>
        <div id="map"></div>
        <div class="map-legend">
          <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot pakomak"></span> Пакомак</div>
          <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot store"></span> Супермаркет</div>
          <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot vending"></span> Автомат</div>
          <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot mall"></span> Мол</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FINANCIAL ===== -->
  <section class="section" id="financial">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2 data-translate-key="section_financial_title">💰 Финансиски Модел</h2>
        <p data-translate-key="section_financial_desc">Платформата е дизајнирана да биде финансиски одржлива и профитабилна за сите учесници.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid var(--accent)">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-percentage"></i> <span data-translate-key="financial_commission">Провизија од Трансакции</span></h4>
            <p data-translate-key="financial_commission_desc">Мала провизија (2-5%) при конверзија на EcoPoints во пари или ваучери. Прозирно и фер.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid var(--accent)">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-ad"></i> <span data-translate-key="financial_ads">Рекламен Простор</span></h4>
            <p data-translate-key="financial_ads_desc">Брендови плаќаат за прикажување на еколошки кампањи. Корисниците добиваат бонус поени.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid var(--accent)">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> <span data-translate-key="financial_partners">Партнерски Провизии</span></h4>
            <p data-translate-key="financial_partners_desc">Провизија од молови и продавници кога корисникот ги користи своите поени кај нив.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid var(--accent)">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-database"></i> <span data-translate-key="financial_data">Анонимизирани Податоци</span></h4>
            <p data-translate-key="financial_data_desc">Агрегирани, анонимизирани податоци за трендови во рециклирањето за истражувачки институции.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h3 style="text-align:center;color:var(--dark);margin:3rem 0 1.5rem;font-size:1.6rem"><i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> <span data-translate-key="financial_payments_title">Интеграција со Платежни Системи</span></h3>
      <p style="text-align:center;color:#666;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem" data-translate-key="financial_payments_desc">Безбедна исплата на заработката преку светски признати платформи. Сите трансакции се енд-ту-енд енкриптирани.</p>
      <div class="payments">
        <div class="payment-badge stripe"><i class="fab fa-stripe"></i> Stripe</div>
        <div class="payment-badge paypal"><i class="fab fa-paypal"></i> PayPal</div>
        <div class="payment-badge visa"><i class="fab fa-cc-visa"></i> Visa Direct</div>
        <div class="payment-badge mastercard"><i class="fab fa-cc-mastercard"></i> Mastercard Send</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f5e9,#d4edda);padding:1.8rem;border-radius:16px;margin-top:2.5rem;border-left:4px solid var(--primary)">
        <strong style="color:var(--primary-dark);display:block;margin-bottom:.8rem;font-size:1.1rem"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> <span data-translate-key="financial_security_title">Финансиска Безбедност на Ниво на Банка</span></strong>
        <span style="color:#555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6"><span data-translate-key="financial_security_desc">Сите платежни процеси се <strong>PCI DSS комплајантни</strong>. Никогаш не чуваме директни податоци од картички – користиме токенизација и енд-ту-енд енкрипција (TLS 1.3+). Регуларни безбедносни аудити од трети страни.</span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== GLOBAL MALLS SECTION ===== -->
  <section class="section" id="global-malls">
    <div class="container">
